1
00:00:07,220 --> 00:00:11,820
♪She looks at the bright moon
hanging high above the clouds♪

2
00:00:11,860 --> 00:00:14,140
♪And I fall into the mountains♪

3
00:00:14,220 --> 00:00:16,100
♪Protect this broken world♪

4
00:00:16,180 --> 00:00:20,620
♪A faint wish♪

5
00:00:20,660 --> 00:00:23,900
♪Life is just a dream,
isn't the world so?♪

6
00:00:23,980 --> 00:00:27,620
♪Looking back,
I count the joys of my remaining years♪

7
00:00:27,700 --> 00:00:31,020
♪It's difficult to see you in my dreams♪

8
00:00:31,060 --> 00:00:33,940
♪Ignoring the coldness of the world,
I still linger♪

9
00:00:33,980 --> 00:00:37,300
♪Love and hate are intertwined,
not just in the past♪

10
00:00:37,340 --> 00:00:40,900
♪The past is painful,
and time goes by in a flash♪

11
00:00:40,940 --> 00:00:44,500
♪Stars fall on the mountain top again♪

12
00:00:44,580 --> 00:00:48,140
♪My heart is as pure as the moon
and connected to you♪

13
00:00:54,140 --> 00:00:56,980
[No One But You]

14
00:00:56,980 --> 00:00:58,620
[Episode 20]

15
00:00:58,620 --> 00:01:00,580
[Luckily, I've never walked
the wrong path.]

16
00:01:00,580 --> 00:01:01,980
[You've never changed either.]

17
00:01:02,900 --> 00:01:05,450
[Missing Person]

18
00:01:37,820 --> 00:01:38,380
You...

19
00:01:49,120 --> 00:01:52,120
[Missing Person: Gu, I'm in Beizhou now.
Meet me at 21 Qinghong Road. - Liu]

20
00:01:56,020 --> 00:01:57,300
Why are you here?

21
00:02:03,980 --> 00:02:05,780
Chihoko and I are getting married.

22
00:02:07,060 --> 00:02:08,620
If you behave,

23
00:02:10,060 --> 00:02:11,940
I promise
she won't give you a hard time.

24
00:02:27,900 --> 00:02:29,540
You want me to be a concubine?

25
00:02:30,380 --> 00:02:31,340
Jerk!

26
00:02:32,660 --> 00:02:33,780
I will never.

27
00:02:37,700 --> 00:02:39,500
Can you tell me

28
00:02:40,780 --> 00:02:42,220
who you are now?

29
00:02:48,700 --> 00:02:51,020
I've had enough patience for you.

30
00:02:51,980 --> 00:02:53,460
Don't be ungrateful.

31
00:02:57,900 --> 00:02:58,980
The lonely boat
has reached the shore.

32
00:03:08,860 --> 00:03:10,780
I am ungrateful, then.

33
00:03:11,420 --> 00:03:12,820
What can you do to me?

34
00:03:13,340 --> 00:03:14,380
Kill me?

35
00:03:17,620 --> 00:03:19,220
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

36
00:03:20,140 --> 00:03:22,500
♪Awakening the jasmine from its slumber♪

37
00:03:22,700 --> 00:03:23,740
One day,

38
00:03:23,780 --> 00:03:25,260
♪Two swallows are building
their nest on the beam♪

39
00:03:25,260 --> 00:03:26,780
I will tame you.

40
00:03:26,780 --> 00:03:29,180
♪Bringing new mud in their beaks♪

41
00:03:30,460 --> 00:03:32,740
I can't drag you into more danger.

42
00:03:32,740 --> 00:03:33,940
♪Where fragrant grass
is growing lush and thick♪

43
00:03:33,940 --> 00:03:34,740
I'm sorry.

44
00:03:35,700 --> 00:03:37,380
I've made you suffer all these years.

45
00:03:38,180 --> 00:03:39,420
Even if I die,

46
00:03:39,940 --> 00:03:40,940
so what?

47
00:03:41,540 --> 00:03:42,580
There is no way.

48
00:03:42,580 --> 00:03:44,580
♪The night wind rises suddenly♪

49
00:03:44,700 --> 00:03:47,460
♪Making the pond water ripple♪

50
00:03:48,260 --> 00:03:51,260
♪I fear most when the full moon occurs♪

51
00:03:51,260 --> 00:03:52,300
From now on,

52
00:03:52,740 --> 00:03:54,660
you won't be fighting alone.

53
00:03:55,420 --> 00:03:56,860
I will be there with you.

54
00:03:56,860 --> 00:03:59,460
♪But hide the traces
of our acquaintance♪

55
00:03:59,500 --> 00:04:01,940
♪Even if my emotions run deep♪

56
00:04:02,060 --> 00:04:05,070
♪How much would you know?♪

57
00:04:05,100 --> 00:04:07,740
♪I gave you a branch of jasmine♪

58
00:04:07,740 --> 00:04:11,220
♪Wishing you would never leave,
staying with me from dawn to dusk♪

59
00:04:11,260 --> 00:04:13,700
♪I never thought we'd part so easily♪

60
00:04:13,780 --> 00:04:17,300
♪While spending forever meeting again♪

61
00:04:17,460 --> 00:04:20,060
♪Why would I not be happy seeing you?♪

62
00:04:20,100 --> 00:04:24,180
♪Willow fluff flew around the city
when we met in haste♪

63
00:04:24,420 --> 00:04:30,380
♪Falling into a dream,
I can still remember this love♪

64
00:04:41,260 --> 00:04:42,300
There are no eyes around here.

65
00:04:42,300 --> 00:04:43,140
It's safe for now.

66
00:04:43,380 --> 00:04:44,100
Okay.

67
00:04:55,380 --> 00:04:56,380
So,

68
00:04:57,420 --> 00:04:58,500
he didn't die.

69
00:05:03,900 --> 00:05:04,700
Qinghuan,

70
00:05:06,260 --> 00:05:08,460
it's time to tell you the whole truth.

71
00:05:09,860 --> 00:05:11,580
I want you to approach this woman.

72
00:05:12,060 --> 00:05:13,420
Fake being hurt

73
00:05:13,420 --> 00:05:14,700
or use your charm, whatever.

74
00:05:15,100 --> 00:05:17,540
Find out who she is.

75
00:05:49,420 --> 00:05:50,380
Why are you here?

76
00:05:51,060 --> 00:05:52,500
Did the Marshal send you here?

77
00:05:53,300 --> 00:05:54,540
He asks me to approach you

78
00:05:55,500 --> 00:05:56,660
and investigate your identity.

79
00:06:04,420 --> 00:06:07,180
So, he's started to suspect me.

80
00:06:09,540 --> 00:06:10,740
Let's play a couple.

81
00:06:12,020 --> 00:06:13,500
I'll do my best to cover for you.

82
00:06:17,300 --> 00:06:19,020
This is Qinghuan, my sister.

83
00:06:19,500 --> 00:06:20,940
She's been studying in another city.

84
00:06:20,940 --> 00:06:24,020
[Yu's Residence]

85
00:06:26,300 --> 00:06:27,340
It's her.

86
00:06:29,940 --> 00:06:30,740
Why?

87
00:06:31,380 --> 00:06:32,300
Do you know her?

88
00:06:36,300 --> 00:06:38,220
This is the girl I told you about.

89
00:06:42,100 --> 00:06:43,100
I didn't know

90
00:06:43,100 --> 00:06:44,460
you had such a connection.

91
00:06:47,660 --> 00:06:48,420
Mohan,

92
00:06:50,180 --> 00:06:51,460
if one day,

93
00:06:51,780 --> 00:06:53,460
anything happens to me,

94
00:06:54,420 --> 00:06:57,060
please take care of Qinghuan for me.

95
00:07:03,500 --> 00:07:05,940
These are my identification documents

96
00:07:05,940 --> 00:07:07,980
and some insignificant information.

97
00:07:10,700 --> 00:07:12,300
It's time to hand me over.

98
00:07:17,780 --> 00:07:19,660
You're asking me to get you killed.

99
00:07:28,140 --> 00:07:28,980
Take it.

100
00:07:32,340 --> 00:07:33,260
Take it!

101
00:07:42,180 --> 00:07:42,940
In fact,

102
00:07:43,700 --> 00:07:44,860
I have been exposed.

103
00:07:45,580 --> 00:07:46,940
The Marshal

104
00:07:46,940 --> 00:07:48,980
is using this to test you.

105
00:07:50,900 --> 00:07:52,940
My death is the last thing I'm worth.

106
00:07:54,100 --> 00:07:55,060
Only in this way,

107
00:07:56,060 --> 00:07:57,300
will you be a dagger

108
00:07:57,300 --> 00:07:58,980
more deeply stabbed
in the enemy's heart.

109
00:08:10,500 --> 00:08:11,460
I've found out.

110
00:08:12,100 --> 00:08:14,020
She's a key member
of the Sparks Society.

111
00:08:14,340 --> 00:08:15,940
This is the intel on her contacts.

112
00:08:21,500 --> 00:08:22,700
I heard

113
00:08:22,700 --> 00:08:24,700
she's now your fiancee.

114
00:08:26,780 --> 00:08:29,700
Are you going to be
that ruthless to her?

115
00:08:30,740 --> 00:08:32,020
You can only get information

116
00:08:32,020 --> 00:08:33,460
with someone's trust.

117
00:08:34,180 --> 00:08:34,940
And love

118
00:08:35,660 --> 00:08:38,940
is the most effective way
to break down someone's defenses.

119
00:08:49,260 --> 00:08:51,140
You know what you are doing.

120
00:08:52,260 --> 00:08:53,420
When it's done,

121
00:08:54,020 --> 00:08:55,460
I'll promote you to Military Governor.

122
00:09:05,450 --> 00:09:10,950
[Merchant Group Wharf]

123
00:09:11,500 --> 00:09:12,660
Hey, Mohan.

124
00:09:32,060 --> 00:09:33,500
I'm thankful that I'll be killed

125
00:09:33,500 --> 00:09:34,780
by my comrade.

126
00:09:36,060 --> 00:09:37,740
I can leave in peace.

127
00:09:56,340 --> 00:09:57,820
No, I can't pull this trigger.

128
00:10:04,260 --> 00:10:05,060
Mohan.

129
00:10:06,500 --> 00:10:07,740
If more people

130
00:10:07,740 --> 00:10:09,260
can live in the light,

131
00:10:09,780 --> 00:10:11,180
my death will be worth it.

132
00:10:12,860 --> 00:10:13,700
I really cannot

133
00:10:13,700 --> 00:10:15,260
shoot at my comrade.

134
00:10:16,100 --> 00:10:17,740
We can fight our way out of here.

135
00:10:17,940 --> 00:10:19,300
If we die, we die together.

136
00:10:21,860 --> 00:10:22,420
Okay.

137
00:10:24,580 --> 00:10:26,060
Let's fight our way out of here.

138
00:10:26,660 --> 00:10:27,420
If we die,

139
00:10:28,420 --> 00:10:29,500
we die together.

140
00:10:30,620 --> 00:10:31,180
Let's go.

141
00:10:58,140 --> 00:10:59,460
Qingqiu!

142
00:11:16,020 --> 00:11:17,740
I owe your sister.

143
00:11:18,500 --> 00:11:19,340
Mohan.

144
00:11:20,580 --> 00:11:21,940
Qingqiu wouldn't blame you.

145
00:11:23,460 --> 00:11:24,340
Because

146
00:11:27,340 --> 00:11:29,900
the one who's been struggling
in the dark

147
00:11:30,460 --> 00:11:31,540
is you.

148
00:11:33,980 --> 00:11:35,060
These years,

149
00:11:35,860 --> 00:11:37,740
my hands have been soaked in blood.

150
00:11:39,020 --> 00:11:41,140
But I've never killed an innocent.

151
00:11:42,420 --> 00:11:43,220
Some

152
00:11:43,780 --> 00:11:45,340
were persecuted by the Marshal.

153
00:11:46,300 --> 00:11:48,060
Some volunteered
to sacrifice their lives.

154
00:11:48,300 --> 00:11:50,940
Others betrayed the Society

155
00:11:51,060 --> 00:11:52,820
so I had to kill them.

156
00:11:52,820 --> 00:11:54,700
I never thought

157
00:11:55,300 --> 00:11:56,940
you'd been carrying so much.

158
00:11:57,900 --> 00:11:59,620
You've been facing
suspicion from the enemy,

159
00:11:59,620 --> 00:12:01,180
the people's scorn,

160
00:12:01,500 --> 00:12:02,700
the hatred from your comrades,

161
00:12:02,700 --> 00:12:03,620
and me,

162
00:12:03,980 --> 00:12:06,340
who tried to kill you again and again.

163
00:12:06,500 --> 00:12:07,420
It's not like that.

164
00:12:07,860 --> 00:12:09,580
The way you hated me
and tried to kill me

165
00:12:10,100 --> 00:12:11,620
was my best cover.

166
00:12:13,420 --> 00:12:14,060
Qinghuan,

167
00:12:15,820 --> 00:12:17,460
I'm sorry
for having made it so hard for you.

168
00:12:19,380 --> 00:12:21,260
You had a bright future.

169
00:12:22,180 --> 00:12:23,220
It was all because of me

170
00:12:23,860 --> 00:12:25,500
who dragged you into the abyss.

171
00:12:26,380 --> 00:12:27,940
I've never walked the wrong path.

172
00:12:28,860 --> 00:12:30,420
You've never changed either.

173
00:12:32,100 --> 00:12:33,780
From now on,

174
00:12:34,860 --> 00:12:36,700
I will walk by your side in this abyss.

175
00:12:37,980 --> 00:12:38,780
Okay.

176
00:12:40,700 --> 00:12:42,740
I will love and protect you
for the rest of my life.

177
00:12:43,700 --> 00:12:44,820
You will be my peace,

178
00:12:45,620 --> 00:12:46,700
and I will never fail you.

179
00:13:30,220 --> 00:13:32,020
♪The blue sea♪

180
00:13:32,060 --> 00:13:34,140
♪Carries the secrets
of the wind in its waves♪

181
00:13:34,220 --> 00:13:38,100
♪But the moon overhears them♪

182
00:13:38,740 --> 00:13:40,900
♪Deep in the sea♪

183
00:13:40,980 --> 00:13:43,260
♪Your fast, gentle fins♪

184
00:13:43,340 --> 00:13:45,900
♪Are out of reach♪

185
00:13:45,980 --> 00:13:47,700
♪I take a leap♪

186
00:13:47,740 --> 00:13:51,340
♪Like the moon embracing the tide♪

187
00:13:51,420 --> 00:13:54,220
♪Fearless of the distance
between the sky and the sea♪

188
00:13:54,340 --> 00:13:59,660
♪Fireflies dancing in the sky
are drawn to you♪

189
00:13:59,740 --> 00:14:03,940
♪Like how I'm captivated by you♪

190
00:14:04,780 --> 00:14:07,180
♪You're from the blue sea♪

191
00:14:07,260 --> 00:14:09,260
♪You don't understand my loneliness♪

192
00:14:09,340 --> 00:14:11,620
♪I wander the earth♪

193
00:14:11,700 --> 00:14:13,740
♪Buying joys for you♪

194
00:14:13,780 --> 00:14:15,420
♪I wish one day♪

195
00:14:15,460 --> 00:14:17,540
♪You will realize♪

196
00:14:17,620 --> 00:14:20,580
♪That I have been living♪

197
00:14:20,660 --> 00:14:22,220
♪Under your eyes♪

198
00:14:22,260 --> 00:14:24,260
♪You're from the blue sea♪

199
00:14:24,300 --> 00:14:26,220
♪You don't understand my loneliness♪

200
00:14:26,300 --> 00:14:28,660
♪I hide in the crowds♪

201
00:14:28,740 --> 00:14:31,100
♪Selling love for you♪

202
00:14:31,180 --> 00:14:33,500
♪If one day you can♪

203
00:14:33,580 --> 00:14:35,540
♪Leap into the sky for me♪

204
00:14:35,620 --> 00:14:41,100
♪You will find traces
of my love for you♪

205
00:15:08,060 --> 00:15:11,780
♪The waves♪

206
00:15:11,860 --> 00:15:16,060
♪When will you stop
looking through them?♪

207
00:15:16,140 --> 00:15:20,100
♪Missed the time
when the sun was restored♪

208
00:15:20,180 --> 00:15:24,260
♪What else do you expect to like?♪

209
00:15:24,300 --> 00:15:27,020
♪I thought you were an angel♪

210
00:15:27,100 --> 00:15:29,300
♪An angel who watched over me♪

211
00:15:29,340 --> 00:15:32,380
♪And saw every side of me♪

212
00:15:32,460 --> 00:15:35,020
♪Until reality is flooded♪

213
00:15:35,100 --> 00:15:37,260
♪You become sensible♪

214
00:15:37,340 --> 00:15:41,820
♪You are finally
out of touch with reality♪

215
00:15:42,140 --> 00:15:44,660
♪I hear the mountains, the seas,
and the people♪

216
00:15:44,740 --> 00:15:46,700
♪All clamoring because of you♪

217
00:15:46,820 --> 00:15:48,780
♪Hiding in the cape after the rain♪

218
00:15:48,940 --> 00:15:51,220
♪I cannot hear you♪

219
00:15:51,260 --> 00:15:54,740
♪So I opened my arms one last time♪

220
00:15:54,900 --> 00:15:58,260
♪But you escaped through the gap♪

221
00:15:58,380 --> 00:16:00,580
♪I saw winters come and summers go♪

222
00:16:00,620 --> 00:16:02,740
♪And thought there was ample time♪

223
00:16:02,980 --> 00:16:04,780
♪Cannot withstand the waves♪

224
00:16:04,900 --> 00:16:06,860
♪But you always make me panic♪

225
00:16:06,940 --> 00:16:11,180
♪How ridiculous, making me learn♪

226
00:16:11,260 --> 00:16:14,540
♪How much I am worth♪
